# Pacman Rule-Based Agents

## Project Description

This project implements several rule-based agents for the Atari MsPacman environment using Gymnasium and ALE.

The goal is to evaluate how different rule-based strategies perform compared to a baseline random agent.

## Environment

The agents interact with the Atari MsPacman environment from the Arcade Learning Environment (ALE).

Environment used:
ALE/MsPacman-v5

